&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The objects are merged from right to left, this means that objects which have identical properties as the objects to their right will be overriden.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In this example &lt;code&gt;obj2.car&lt;/code&gt; overrides &lt;code&gt;obj1.car&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Wow.. this is the first StackOverflow post I&apos;ve seen with multiple pages. Apologies for adding another &quot;answer&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
